rows.label: tlk70000003_05_msg0001
rows.name:
You helped make Iiran research
big success for Dekudeku,
but now nearing end.

rows.label: tlk70000003_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Dekudeku always thought that
key to trade was to have novel
idea and information...

rows.label: tlk70000003_05_msg0003
rows.name:
But watching you, can tell
that most important is
connections between people...

rows.label: tlk70000003_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Learned all this after coming to Iira!
Also learned to love this town!

rows.label: tlk70000003_05_msg0005
rows.name:
But Dekudeku is trader! And
soon must leave for new town
to broaden horizons further!

rows.label: tlk70000003_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Not worry! No matter where
in Alst travels take
Dekudeku, not forget you!

rows.label: tlk70000003_05_msg0007
rows.name:
You are Dekudeku's best
friends in all of Iira!
